    <sys:String x:Key="Main.SpecialVersion.DebugHint">The current PCL Community Edition build is a Debug build.&#x0a;This build is only intended for developer debugging and may have serious performance issues or various unexpected network problems.&#x0a;&#x0a;Problems caused by non-developer users running this build are not supported by the community, and related issues may be closed directly.&#x0a;Unless you are a developer, please delete this build immediately and use the latest stable version instead.</sys:String>
