    <sys:String x:Key="Setup.GameManage.Download.FixAuthlib.ToolTip">Some Minecraft versions, such as 1.16.5, have a bug that may cause multiplayer to be disabled when using offline login.&#x0a;PCL can try to upgrade the Authlib support library for these versions to fix the issue.&#x0a;This setting only applies to newly installed instances.</sys:String>
